      "instruction": "<p>Drain the<strong> tofu</strong> and cut lengthways into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> slices, then pat dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced tofu</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half </strong>the<strong> soy sauce</strong> (save the rest for later!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>marinated tofu</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to a plate</p><p>Press the<strong> marinated tofu </strong>into the panko breadcrumbs firmly, until evenly coated all over – this is your <strong>coated tofu</strong></p>",
