      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated tofu</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until golden and crispy all over, then transfer to a plate lined with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper and reserve the pan – this is your <strong>crispy tofu</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
