    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tofu is cooking, peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and roughly chop the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and roughly chop the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p>",
