    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, add the <strong>wholewheat noodles </strong>and cook for 2 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>While the noodles are cooking, wash, then, slice the <strong>pak choi</strong> in quarters lengthways and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
