    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the noodles are beginning to soften, add the <strong>pak choi quarters </strong>and cook for 4-5 min further</p><p>After 4-5 min, add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min or until the noodles are cooked with a slight bite, the pak choi is tender and the spinach has wilted – this is your <strong>fragrant coconut ramen</strong></p>",
