      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> fragrant coconut ramen </strong>in a bowl and top<strong> </strong>with the <strong>crispy tofu</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
